div.form-element
  label(for="gtin13") gtin13
  input(type="text", id="gtin13", name="gtin13", placeholder="gtin13")
  div.description The GTIN-13 code of the product, or the product to which the offer refers. This is equivalent to 13-digit ISBN codes and EAN UCC-13. Former 12-digit UPC codes can be converted into a GTIN-13 code by simply adding a preceeding zero.